{"tid":2278627,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"為抗疫掟石驅趕野鳥 退休漢被判監禁6星期","createTime":"2020-11-09T09:28:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T16:26:43.000Z","uid":240362,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"a21b6b9e10092fb7563048e33b13c9e9e8f920a7","tid":2278627,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T09:28:12.000Z","msg":"退休老翁聲稱從電台廣播得知野鳥會帶來病毒，為防止路人接觸野鳥，他自創向野鳥投石抗疫大法。今年4月，他向粉嶺公路一段隔音屏障投擲石塊以驅趕野鳥，其間被巡警發現拘捕。老翁早前在粉嶺裁判法院承認一項公眾地方妨擾罪，今被判囚6星期。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官黃國輝判刑時指，涉案石塊體積頗大，尤幸石塊受隔音屏阻擋；石塊一旦飛出公路，撞上汽車擋風玻璃，勢釀成嚴重交通意外。鑑於案情嚴重，故判被告即時監禁。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201109/TMQE3RWGTJDTXPT3JOAOP7SW2A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201109%2FTMQE3RWGTJDTXPT3JOAOP7SW2A%2F&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2BejOHetkdf0TruP2VOJ8R9E%3D&h=fd3f83eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201109%2FTMQE3RWGTJDTXPT3JOAOP7SW2A%2F&h=d97c851c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201109/TMQE3RWGTJDTXPT3JOAOP7SW2A/</a>"},{"pid":"bdb5dc0d50a628ad9b0f7977bbd4582c98b59569","tid":2278627,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T09:29:28.000Z","msg":"終於抗到疫了"},{"pid":"a8546f2aaa9142c2fc6a8a748f32c8a49acf011a","tid":2278627,"uid":70786,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T09:32:29.000Z","msg":"死廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個官又憑幻想判刑<br />\n假設石頭飛出去影響行車安全？"},{"pid":"0aced4fa0ce270522d3e203a4087057d9e66416b","tid":2278627,"uid":57488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T09:33:44.000Z","msg":"死廢老<br />\n唔出街咪無事囉"},{"pid":"02ade4b4e5d5d3a3886aef59646d426f1e6d45b4","tid":2278627,"uid":42250,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T09:33:49.000Z","msg":"有冇內情呀咁都6星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b9b2ad